  "3136130": {
    "name": "Metroloop",
    "steam_appid": 3136130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/81024596b9387c45d998706d8b025229.avif?t=1734019957\" width=614 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the furthest stations in the postapocalyptic top down shooter and platformer looter. Loot tunnels in side scrolling mode and survive from waves of monsters on the stations in a top down twin stick shooter mode. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far will you go?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/7b19cd40dde039b4ed57bb46ca96de8e.apng?t=1734019957\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/7b19cd40dde039b4ed57bb46ca96de8e.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy boxes to find crucial loot in tunnels, between stations. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boxes contain upgrades, weapons, ammo and coins and you have only 40 seconds to find whatever you need during platformer tunnel phase. Light shuts down every 5 seconds, during which you will have to move forward.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrading your axe skill will make smashing boxes faster. Keys found in monsters bodies will open boxes faster.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/f9e88556cec81c46c2ed8bb52f0d75ce.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" width=612 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/f9e88556cec81c46c2ed8bb52f0d75ce.webm?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/f9e88556cec81c46c2ed8bb52f0d75ce.mp4?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/94d71a450fb078d03f45726dee6bf99e.webp?t=1734019957\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/94d71a450fb078d03f45726dee6bf99e.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot your way through stations in a top down twin-stick shooter phase of the game.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Quantity and thoughness of enemies go slowly up with every next station, along your upgrades and weapons. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 different types of enemies will be waiting for you at the stations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can hold and use two weapons at the same time, manage your ammo responsibly. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally you will have special abilities at your disposal, such as landmines, shield, glue trap and teleporter, that will help you leave every station alive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/3b7abe9cc8323e3fdd904db9896e9a50.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" width=612 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/3b7abe9cc8323e3fdd904db9896e9a50.webm?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/3b7abe9cc8323e3fdd904db9896e9a50.mp4?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/8b4e4c41bc268ed75906fefd27baecb2.webp?t=1734019957\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/8b4e4c41bc268ed75906fefd27baecb2.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade temporarily and permanently.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open boxes with green arrows to find upgrades of your skills and weapons. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each upgrade improves your stats by small amount but you can keep upgrading endlessly. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy permanent weapon upgrades for collected coins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock achievements for permanent upgrades of your character's skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/833850369006e027c97cbedf6e704a29.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/833850369006e027c97cbedf6e704a29.webm?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/833850369006e027c97cbedf6e704a29.mp4?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/17a5fa06c3230dfd4bca9ffe0466388a.webp?t=1734019957\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/17a5fa06c3230dfd4bca9ffe0466388a.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive as many stations as possible.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting enemies will not always be the best solution, sometimes you can avoid them or run away from them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/2e0b70c08f640d08ddef30c03831ab2b.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" width=612 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/2e0b70c08f640d08ddef30c03831ab2b.webm?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/2e0b70c08f640d08ddef30c03831ab2b.mp4?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every tunnel has a healing chamber at the end of it. The more time you will save, the more life points you will restore before all lights shut down.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/62670afa8e4fcd5f366e3ec3fb3cfcc8.poster.avif?t=1734019957\" width=612 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/62670afa8e4fcd5f366e3ec3fb3cfcc8.webm?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136130/extras/62670afa8e4fcd5f366e3ec3fb3cfcc8.mp4?t=1734019957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
